            {
              "mark": "A1",
              "desc": "1:2.25 or 4:9"
            }
          ],
          "workingSteps": [
            "Area scale factor = |SF|² = 1.5² = 2.25",
            "Ratio = 1:2.25 = 4:9"
          ]
        },
        {
          "label": "c",
          "questionText": "Triangle P is reflected in the line $y = x$ to give triangle Q.\nWork out the vertices of triangle Q.",
